   // Set -->                   HashSet, LinkedHashSet, TreeSet, EnumSet
Maintains insertion order         no        yes            no      no
Sorted order                       no         no          yes        yes(ordinal) 
thread safe                       no        no             no         no


synchronisation by adding external wrapper
Collection.synchronizedSet(any set you can pass) the resulting return set will be synchronised
very bad use of this instead use ConcurrentSkipListSet


//set extends collections
//hash keys are infact set only

ConcurrentSkipListSet--while iterating and when its on the last index,and you are adding one more value, it might iterate or it might not
so better use CopyOnWriteSet



